  "instructions": [
    "Season the chicken thighs with salt, pepper, smoked paprika, cumin, and chili powder.",
    "Heat a grill or grill pan over medium‑high heat and lightly oil the grates with olive oil.",
    "Grill the chicken for 5–6 minutes per side, or until an instant‑read thermometer reads 165 °F (74 °C).",
    "While the chicken rests, whisk together heavy cream, yogurt, mustard, cocoa powder, and a pinch of salt to make the sauce.",
